from La Mesa. ; Photo, Riding the trolley gives passengers a chance to catch up 
on reading, and Bernetta Puryear, above, tackles the newspaper on a ride 
downtown. The trolley, which now extends east to La Mesa, pulls into downtown's 
Civic Center stop, below. STAN HONDA 
</P>
